id: pm-github-o7jl
title: Search provider maps remote matches to LOCAL items only
description: "pm runtime drops provider hits whose id is not a local document (normalizeExtensionProviderHits). So the github provider queries GitHub for the repo, then returns hits ONLY for issues that are already imported locally (matched by provenance tag). Semantics: 'find my imported items whose upstream issue matches this query'. Provider runs only in semantic/hybrid mode. Add 'search' to manifest only after verifying it activates + returns hits."
